{"tid":927413,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港真係米線之都黎,實有間係你附近","createTime":"2018-12-04T06:54:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T11:39:26.000Z","uid":119688,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"735d36f948cefd5783b3a4a336b3c92d35092c03","tid":927413,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:54:53.000Z","msg":"以前條街邊有咁多<br />\n近呢十年真係多過7仔ok<br />\n<br />\n以前對米線麻麻 覺得唔飽肚<br />\n成日心諗自己屋企煮都得<br />\n但條街選擇越黎越少<br />\n加上朋友圈,自己都慢慢上左癮<br />\n自此白飯真心好少食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n出轉油麻地至深水埗 幾個胃都食唔哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e4d09e441f00148cf899e6f58bd6d86110591e6","tid":927413,"uid":34676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"好食既又好少呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"688961de704b7a7e15b22d134259ddd9ae6c17d7","tid":927413,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"1e4d09e441f00148cf899e6f58bd6d86110591e6","tid":927413,"uid":34676,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:55:35.000Z","msg":"好食既又好少呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:56:17.000Z","msg":"我出呢個post既同時都食緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79a37b5939334e2431a44e9af0acd531da9f5c9f","tid":927413,"uid":217940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T06:57:41.000Z","msg":"食完好快又餓返"},{"pid":"e20c5e908ca778c8c916964b9584f951ad2c10bd","tid":927413,"uid":119688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"79a37b5939334e2431a44e9af0acd531da9f5c9f","tid":927413,"uid":217940,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"rep